# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Environment variable template for E-COM Analytics

# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Create a file called `.Renviron` in the project root.
# 2. Use this template to set system variables securely.
# 3. Replace the placeholder values with your own credentials.
# 4. Restart R / RStudio before running any scripts.

# NOTE:
# - This file is a template and is safe to commit.
# - The actual `.Renviron` file is ignored by Git.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------

MYSQL_HOST=localhost
MYSQL_USER=your_mysql_username
MYSQL_PASSWORD=your_mysql_password
